<HR NOSHADE SIZE=4>
<FONT SIZE=5><b><A NAME="district">Districts</A></b></FONT><BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE=3>Members of the Association are also members of the Districts in which they do business. The Districts carry forward on a local basis the work of SIA in such areas as government relations, economic education, professional education and public information. Each District has its own executive committee and budget.  SIA staff liaison for District activities is <A HREF=mailto:rgannon@sia.com>Rob Gannon.</A></FONT><p><br>
