<P>
<FONT  SIZE=-1><B><SUP>1</SUP></B></FONT> 115 S.Ct. 1920 (1995).
<P>
<FONT  SIZE=-1><B><SUP>2</SUP></B></FONT> 475 U.S. 643, 649 (1986).
<P>
<FONT  SIZE=-1><B><SUP>3</SUP></B></FONT> Edward D. Jones & Co. v. Sorrells 957 F.2d 509 (7th Cir. 1992).<BR>
PaineWebber Inc. v. Hartmann 921 F.2d 507 (3rd Cir. 1990).<BR>
Roney & Co. v. Kassab 981 F.2d 894 (6th Cir. 1990).<BR>
Cogswell v. Merrill Lynch 78 F.3d 474 (10th Cir. 1996).<BR>
Merrill Lynch v. Cohen 62 F.3d 381 (11th Cir. 1995).
