<DOCNO>WT07-B27-62</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA031-000653-B007-61</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sia.com:80/sia09d.htm 199.170.0.177 19970122123033 text/html 3842
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 22 Jan 1997 12:30:35 GMT
