<P>
<HR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+3><B>Survey</B></FONT></CENTER>
<FONT  SIZE=-1><P></FONT>
<HR>
<P>
The following survey was created at the suggestion of the Year 2000 Sub-Committee.  The survey is for SIA Member Firms ONLY.  It will promote awareness, draw attention to issues involved in Year 2000 compliance, and allow the Data Management Division to gauge member readiness.  All responses will be kept confidential.
<P>
<CENTER>Please print out this survey, complete it, and return to:
<P>
<B>Mr. Thomas Duffy<BR>
c/o CS First Boston Inc.  - 7th Floor<BR>
Five World Trade Center<BR>
New York, NY  10048</B></CENTER>
<P>

<P>
