<HEAD>
<TITLE>Year 2000 Project Plan</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<body background="sia3abac.gif">
<FONT SIZE=+4><B><EM><FONT  COLOR="#0000C0">Year 2000</FONT></EM></FONT><BR><HR NO SHADE=2>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+3>Project Plan</FONT></CENTER></B>
<P><HR NO SHADE=2>
This is a proposed plan developed to assist the financial community in its preparation for the Year 2000.
It is not meant to be a comprehensive plan and actions can vary depending on a firm, but the plan 
does provide the key steps that should be taken to successfully prepare for the Year 2000.<P>
<TABLE COLSPEC="L20 L20 L20" BORDER=2 WIDTH=100%>
<TR><TD><STRONG>Action</STRONG></TD><TD><STRONG>Start Date</STRONG></TD><TD><STRONG>Finish Date</STRONG></TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Select a steering committee</TD><TD>Jan 1996</TD><TD>Jan 1996</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Appoint a project manager</TD><TD>Feb 1996</TD><TD>Feb 1996</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Evaluate how extensive your conversion will be</TD><TD>Apr 1996</TD><TD>Jun 1996</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Select a tool to help automate the conversion</TD><TD>Apr 1996</TD><TD>Jul 1996</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Prepare and distribute an RFP for the outside services you will require</TD><TD>Jul 1996</TD><TD>Jul 1996</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Select an outside firm to provide the services you require</TD><TD>Jul 1996</TD><TD>Sep 1996</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Determine if all your vendor-supplied software is year 200 compliant</TD><TD>Jul 1996</TD><TD>Sep 1996</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Prioritize and plan the order of conversion for your sub-systems</TD><TD>Jul 1996</TD><TD>Oct 1996</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Develop time, cost and resource plan for the conversion</TD><TD>Aug 1996</TD><TD>Nov 1996</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Source code and "JCL" changes completed</TD><TD>Jan 1997</TD><TD>Jun 1997</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>File and database conversion completed</TD><TD>Jan 1997</TD><TD>Jan 1998</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>All source code modifications unit tested</TD><TD>Mar 1997</TD><TD>Jan 1998</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Integration test of sub-systems completed</TD><TD>May 1997</TD><TD>May 1998</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>All documentation updates completed</TD><TD>May 1997</TD><TD>Jun 1998</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>User acceptance testing completed</TD><TD>Jul 1997</TD><TD>Sep 1998</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Parallel test of all sub-systems completed</TD><TD>Sep 1997</TD><TD>Dec 1998</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Move converted applications to production environment</TD><TD>Nov 1997</TD><TD>Jan 1999</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Complete street-wide testing</TD><TD>Mar 1999</TD><TD>Jun 1999</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=1>
