<TITLE>Credit Division</TITLE>
<body background="sia3abac.gif"><IMG SRC="siaband.gif" ALT="Securities Industry Association"><BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE=+4><B><I> About The Credit Division</I></B></FONT><BR><BR>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=4>
<FONT SIZE=+2><B>Mission</B></FONT><P>
<LH></LH>
The objectives and functions of the division are:
<P>
<UL>
<LI>Improve business practices and quality of service in its area of expertise, promote high standards of professional capability and performances, foster efficient operations, and where applicable, encourage uniformity of practice.<BR>
<LI>Provide a medium for the exchange of ideas and experiences.<BR>
<LI>Develop policy positions with regulatory and self-regulatory bodies.<BR>
<LI>Provide the Federal Reserve Board, Securities and Exchange Commission, New York Stock Exchange and other self-regulatory bodies with information, guidance and opinions with respect to the interpretation and implementation of new, proposed or existing rules.<BR>
<LI>Maintain liaison with SIA, other SIA Divisions and securities industry organizations.
</UL>
<P>
