<TITLE>CAT Division</TITLE>
<body background="sia3abac.gif"><IMG SRC="siaband.gif" ALT="Securities Industry Association"><BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE=+4><B><I> About The Customer Account Transfer Division</I></B></FONT><BR><BR>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=4>
<FONT SIZE=+2><B>Mission</B></FONT><P>
<P>
The Customer Account Transfer (CAT) Division is an organization whose goal is to provide clients with efficient and timely account transfers within the financial community. The CAT Division encourages open lines of communication between firms in a professional team environment in order to provide optimal service in regards to the transfer requests of our clients.
<P>
The division reviews all major regulatory initiatives for their operational consequences, issuing formal comment when needed and/or initiating AD Hoc committees to revise policies and develop technical recommendations.
<P>
For your information and review, <a href="sia01ffb.htm">CAT DIVISION NEWS</a> is available.
