<TITLE>Dividend Division</TITLE>
<body background="sia3abac.gif"><IMG SRC="siaband.gif" ALT="Securities Industry Association"><BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE=+4><B><I> About The Dividend Division</I></B></FONT><BR><BR>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=4>
<FONT SIZE=+2><B>Mission</B></FONT><P>
The primary objective of the organization is the development of greater efficiency and uniformity of practice in the handling of dividends and bond interest and other related distributions by banking institutions and brokerage firms.  A second and no less important objective of this organization is the promotion of a spirit of cooperation and goodwill among dividend and bond interest specialists holding similar positions of responsibility in banking institutions and brokerage firms.
With all of the tax ramifications on income and with the income processing world vastly growing to include global securities, the Dividend Division has been required to upgrade its focus to adapt to these highly specialized areas, and prepare for future changes.<P>
