<TITLE>Securities Operations Division</TITLE>
<body background="sia3abac.gif"><IMG SRC="siaband.gif" ALT="Securities Industry Association"><BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE=+4><B><I> About The Securities Operations Division</I></B></FONT><BR><BR>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=4>
<FONT SIZE=+2><B>Mission</B></FONT><P>
The primary objective of this organization is the development of greater efficiency and uniformity of practice by banking and brokerage firms, and to further this objective through the use of educational means available to the division.  A secondary and no less important objective of this organization is the promotion of a spirit of cooperation and goodwill among persons holding positions of responsibility in baning and brokerage firms.<P>
