<P>
The hotel space that SIA was able to obtain forces us to limit registration.  Accordingly, it is strongly recommended that you register now.  Registration is limited to SIA members and employees of regulatory, clearing and depository organizations.  For your convenience, the <A HREF="int-reg.htm">conference registration form</A> and <A HREF="int-form.htm">hotel & travel information</A> is also available.
