<body background="sia3abac.gif"><IMG SRC="sialog.gif" ALT="Securities Industry Association"><BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE=+4><B><I>Subscriptions</I></B></FONT><BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE=3>SIA maintains a mailing list database of its membership. If your name is not on our free list and would like to subscribe to any of the services below, simply complete an <A HREF="siapub11.htm">order form.</A>  Note, the dollar figure shown is an annual per name charge.  Renewal notices are sent to the subscribing individual.  Please add $12 (to defray postage) for any address outside the Continental U.S. and Canada.  All checks should be made payable to the Securities Industry Association and sent to the attention of <A HREF=mailto:sserpico@sia.com>Suzanne Serpico</A> at 120 Broadway, 35th floor, New York, NY 10271-0080.</FONT><P>
