<P>
<CENTER><FONT  SIZE=+2><B>Nine Industry Executives Elected as SIA Directors</B></FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<dd><STRONG>Boca Raton, FL</STRONG> -- The following nine securities industry executives were today elected as directors of the Securities Industry Association to serve three-year terms ending December 1999:
<P>
<UL>
<LI><B>Mark E. Lehman</B>, Executive Vice President<BR>The Bear Stearns Companies, Inc., New York, NY
<LI><B>Bernard L. Madoff</B>, Principal<BR>Bernard L. Madoff Investment Securities, New York, NY
