<LI><B>John L. Steffens</B>, Executive Vice President, Private Client<BR>Merrill Lynch & Co., Inc., New York, NY
<LI><B>Mark B. Sutton</B>, Director of Private Client Group<BR>PaineWebber Group, Inc., New York, NY
<LI><B>Robert W. Kampmeinert</B>, Chairman, President and CEO<BR>Parker/Hunter Incorporated, Pittsburgh, PA
<LI><B>Sherif A. Nada</B>, President<BR>Fidelity Brokerage Group, Boston, MA
<LI><B>James W. Stuckert</B>, Chairman and CEO<BR>J.J.B. Hilliard, W.L. Lyons, Inc., Louisville, KY
<LI><B>Wilbert A. Thiel</B>, President and COO<BR>The Chicago Corporation, Chicago, IL
</UL>
<P>
Madoff, Paton, Steffens and Nada are continuing on the Board.	
<P>
Mr. Sutton is filling the remaining term of Roy J. Zuckerberg, who has been nominated as vice chairman.  The term expires in December 1998.
<P>
The directors whose terms continue until December 1997 are:
<P>
<UL>
<LI><B>Bernard B. Beal</B>, Chief Executive Officer<BR>M.R. Beal & Company, New York, NY
<LI><B>Daniel H. Case III</B>, President, CEO<BR>Hambrecht & Quist,  Inc., San Francisco, CA
<LI><B>Max Chapman</B>, Co-Chairman and Co-CEO<BR>Nomura Securities International, Inc., New York, NY
<LI><B>Francis S. Godbold</B>, President <BR>Raymond James Financial, Inc., St. Petersburg, FL
<LI><B>Robert N. Gordon</B>, President<BR>Twenty-First Securities Corporation, New York, NY
<LI><B>David D. Lewis</B>, Co-Chief Operating Officer<BR>Ragen McKenzie Incorporated, Seattle, WA
<LI><B>Robert M. Murphy</B>, President, RPM Specialist Corporation<BR>McCooey Clearing Corporation, New York, NY
<LI><B>Rudolph C. Sander</B>, Chairman of the Board<BR>Janney Montgomery Scott Inc., Philadelphia, PA
</UL>
<P>
The directors whose terms continue until December 1998 are:
<P>
<UL>
<LI><B>Frank E. Baxter</B>, President and CEO<BR>Jefferies & Co., Inc., Los Angeles, CA
<LI><B>Lilia C. Clemente</B>, Chairman and CEO<BR>Clemente Fund Management Inc., New York, NY
