<LI>Year 2000 Project Plan - The Committee voted to accept the Plan as distributed. This document presents guidelines suggested by the Year 2000 Committee for the following Year 2000 areas: (1) Project Scope and Components, (2) Target Dates and (3) GANTT Chart of Target Dates and Components
<LI>SyncSort - Year 2000 Sort Enhancement Overview: (1) Requires 3.6 version of SyncSort and (2) Describes 'control statements to SORT, MERGE, OUTREC and OUTFIL OUTREC files which only have a 2 position year into correct sequences for turn of the century' 
