<title>Trends</title>
<BODY><body background="#FFFFFF"><br>
<IMG SRC="siatrd.gif" ><BR><BR>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=1>&copy; 1996 Securities Industry Association
</A><A HREF="sia00.htm"><IMG Border=0 ALIGN=right SRC="siahome.gif" ALT="Homepage"></A><A HREF="siapub2.htm"><IMG Border=0 ALIGN=right SRC="ballleft.gif" ALT="Previous"></A></BODY></HTML>
