<DOCNO>WT07-B27-194</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA030-000646-B014-191</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sia.com:80/sia06aa.htm 199.170.0.177 19970122131316 text/html 9474
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 22 Jan 1997 13:13:15 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.3
Content-type: text/html
