<DOCHDR>
http://abacus.me.berkeley.edu:80/BERC/Projects/Alameda/index.html 128.32.14.93 19970109232537 text/html 6623
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.4 ID/37
Message-ID: <aefabee9.303@abacus.me.berkeley.edu>
