<li> Graduated Summa Cum Laude from Texas A&M, GPA 3.97/4.00
<li> Outstanding Senior, Texas A&M Department of Nuclear Engineering
<li> National Academy for Nuclear Training Undergraduate Scholarship
<li> Dean's List, Academic Incentive Award, Academic Excellence Award
