<!-- Page Title: MATECH: Fluorescent Reference Products -->
<!-- HTML Author: Ahmed A. Enany              -->
<!-- Graphics: Ahmed A. Enany                 -->
<!-- Copyright owner: MATECH                        -->
<!-- E-Mail: matech@sure.net                                 -->
<!-- **************************************** -->
<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>MATECH: Fluorescent Reference Products</TITLE></HEAD><Meta name="description" content="MATECH manufactures 96 wellplate reader reference plates for the calibration of plate reading machines."></HEAD>

<Body Background="dna.gif">
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=483 align=right>
<TD WIDTH=483>
<CENTER><img src="logo3.jpg" Width= 400 Height=78 Alt="Logo"></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><img src="slidbar.gif" Width=398 Height=4 Alt="Animated Bar"></CENTER>
<BR><BR>

<CENTER><H1><FONT SIZE=5 Face="Arial"><B>FLUORESCENT REFERENCE PRODUCTS</B></FONT></H1></CENTER><BR>
<FONT SIZE=4 FACE="ARIAL">MATECH manufactures 96 wellplate reader reference plates for the calibration of plate reading machines which are marketed by <B>Spec Check</B> (Fullerton, CA). These solid-state reference products are for fluorescent-based analytical and clinical instruments. 96 well assay plates are used in a wide variety  of testing procedures, including tests for HIV antibodies and DNA analysis. <BR>
<P></P>
<CENTER><img src="plate.gif" Width=269 Height=196 Alt="Picture of a fluorescent plate"></CENTER>
<P></P>
The reference plates help assure reliable measurements by checking the alignment of plate readers, comparing the intensity of different instruments, and documenting the intensity of excitation sources. <BR><BR>
For more information on fluorescent reference products, write to :<BR></FONT>

<CENTER><table bgcolor="#FFFF80">
<td>
<FONT SIZE=4 FACE="ARIAL">Ed Pope, President,<BR>
MATECH,<BR>
31304 Via Colinas, Ste. 102, <BR>
Westlake Village, CA 91362. <BR><BR></FONT>
<CENTER><table bgcolor="#FF8080">
<td>
<CENTER><FONT FACE="ARIAL"><B>PHN: (818) 991-8500</B><BR>
<B>FAX: (818) 991-4134</FONT></B><BR><BR><BR></CENTER>
</td></table></CENTER>
</td></table></CENTER>

