Software Engineer <BR>

Medical Marketing/Business Development Intern (UCLA, USC or Cal State System)<BR>

Please call Susan Gross, Human Resources Manager, at (310) 643-5106<BR><BR>

<hr>

<CENTER><A NAME="Jump 2"><B><FONT SIZE =4><a href="http://www.jobbrowser.com">The Partners</a></FONT></B></CENTER><BR>
<FONT FACE="ARIAL"><I>(Posted by request on Dec. 6, 1996)</I><BR><BR>
We have a current opening for a Sr. Software Engineer in Southern
California along the Beach Cities in Los Angeles. The qualifed
applicant will have a background developing application software
in a Windows95/NT environment using C/C++, GUI, object-oriented
design environment. The candidate will have a minimum BSCS or 
BSEE with the equivelent of 5+ yrs. of  related experience in 
medical software development, PC networks and Database Design.
Mac and PC hardware knowledge desirable.<BR><BR>

Please contact:<BR>

Tim Nelson<BR>
(310) 225-2900 (Voice)<BR>
(310) 225-2901 (Fax Resume)<BR>
Email to <a href="mailto:TNT1842@aol.com">TNT1842@aol.com</a></FONT>
