<CENTER><H3>SUBMITTING INFORMATION TO SCBC'S CLASSIFIED SECTION</H3></CENTER>
<BR><BR>

<FORM METHOD="POST" ACTION="/cgi-bin/comments.exe">

<input type="hidden" name="to" value="scbc@socalbio.org">
<input type="hidden" name="nextpage" value="http://www.socalbio.org/mail.htm">
Please Enter your e-mail address before you proceed:<input type="text" name="email" size=40>
<P>
1- Company name:<BR>
<INPUT NAME="COMPANY" TYPE=TEXT MAXLENGTH=50 SIZE=50><BR><BR>
2- Contact name:<BR>
<INPUT NAME="CONTACT" TYPE=TEXT MAXLENGTH=50 SIZE=50><BR><BR>
3- Title:<BR>
<INPUT NAME="TITLE" TYPE=TEXT MAXLENGTH=50 SIZE=50><BR><BR>
4- Street address:<BR>
<INPUT NAME="STREET" TYPE=TEXT MAXLENGTH=50 SIZE=50><BR><BR>
5- City:<BR>
<INPUT NAME="CITY" TYPE=TEXT MAXLENGTH=30 SIZE=30><BR><BR>
6- State:<BR>
<INPUT NAME="STATE" TYPE=TEXT MAXLENGTH=10 SIZE=10><BR><BR>
7- Zip code:<BR>
<INPUT NAME="Zip" TYPE=TEXT MAXLENGTH=10 SIZE=10><BR><BR>
8- Phone number:<BR>
<INPUT NAME="PHONE" TYPE=TEXT MAXLENGTH=20 SIZE=20><BR><BR>
9- Fax number:<BR>
<INPUT NAME="FAX" TYPE=TEXT MAXLENGTH=20 SIZE=20><BR><BR>
10- How long do you want your notice or ad to be posted (# of months) :<BR>
<INPUT NAME="months" TYPE=TEXT MAXLENGTH=20 SIZE=20><BR><BR>
11- Notice or ad to be Posted :<BR>
<TEXTAREA NAME="adtext" ROWS=20 COLS=65></TEXTAREA><BR><BR>
<HR>
<CENTER><INPUT TYPE="SUBMIT" VALUE="Submit"></CENTER>
</FORM>

<BR><BR>

<B>Policy and Guidelines:</B><BR>
Fill out the following form to include your information in SCBC's on-line classified section. You have to provide an e-mail address below for your request to be processed. When done click on the "Submit" button below to send information to SCBC.
<P>
Notice that you are responsible for the accuracy of the information submitted. Posting a note in SCBC's classified section does not imply any endorsement by SCBC of your organization or the products, services, and resources wanted or offered. SCBC reserves the right to refuse posting any inappropriate notices on its on-line classified section.
<P>
<B>Charges:</B><BR>
Members of the Southern California Biomedical Council can utilize SCBC's classified section at any time free-of-charge. Individuals looking for biomedical jobs can also post notices free-of-charge.
<P>
If your organization is not a member of the Southern California Biomedical Council, the following charges will apply for utilizing SCBC's classified section:
<UL><LI>You will pay ten cents per word for a notice to be posted for a month (30 days). After a month, the notice will be removed automatically unless otherwise indicated below.
<LI>If you indicate that you want your notice to be posted for more than one month, you will pay ten cents per word for the first month and $5 per each subsequent month.
<LI> Additional charges will apply, if you want graphics included with your notice.</UL>

<BR><BR>

