<P>
<UL>
<li><a href="http://www.achoo.com">Achoo - Healthcare Directory</A>
<li><a href="http://www.bio.com/">Bio Online</a> - a comprehensive web site for biotechnology-related information and services.
<li><a href="http://www.catosource.com/">CatoSource</a> - business-to-business directory of products and services  for biotechnology and pharmaceutical development. 
<li><a href="http://www.biotechinfo.com/">Institute for Biotechnology Information</a> - located in North Carolina's Research Triangle Park and provides proprietary databases and other information about U.S. biotech companies and international business activities. 
<li><a href="http://www.infohwy.com/business/iei/">IEI Publishing</a> - Oil, Gas, Petrochemical, Biotechnology, and Environmental Industry Directories. Each directory lists thousands of companies. 
<li><a href="http://www.luxnet.com">LuxNet</a> - Provides news, and information for professionals and managers in the biosciences--medical device, biotechnology and pharmaceutical companies. LuxNet provides critical and timely information to business professionals to assist them in managing their businesses better.  The company also provides a detailed summary of the most important 50 news articles every morning, a summary of newly issued patents within 12 hours of their issue, and a database of over 350 (and growing) companies who provide important services to the biosciences.
<li><a href="http://pharminfo.com/drugpr/dexfen_pr.html">Pharmaceutical and Biotechnology Press Releases</a>
</UL>
<P>

<CENTER><B><U>Biomedical/Biotechnology Firms on the Web</U></B></CENTER>
<P>
<UL>
<li><a href="http://www.alsbyte.com">ALSBYTE Biotechnology Reagents and Software</a> - Reagents & software for biotech researchers.  Applications include cloning, image analysis,  fingerprinting, and DNA sequencing.  

<li><a href="http://www.amresco-inc.com/">AMRESCO</a> - manufacturer of reagents and chemicals for the clinical  diagnostic, histology and biotechnology industries.  

<li><a href="http://www.asi.bc.ca/bcba/angiotech/">Angiogenesis Technologies Inc</a> - a  biotechnology company engaged in the development of  innovative treatments for cancer, arthritis and other  angiogenesis dependent diseases.  

<li><a href="http://www.bionexus.com/">Bio\Nexus, Inc.</a> - bio-technology company providing services to the rehabilitation community.

<li><a href="http://www.biosource.com/">Biosource International</a> - a publicly traded (NASDAQ BIOI) company specializing in  biotechnology products for academic, institutional, and  commercial research.  

<li><a href="http://www.biosource-bti.com/">Biosource Technologies, Inc.</a> - development and implementation of new biotechnology products through its proprietary Geneware expression system.

<li><a href="http://www-leland.stanford.edu/~ziv/">Biotest, Inc.</a> - offers pre clinical and clinical laboratory testing to assist in biotechnology and pharmaceutical company product development and trial.

<li><a href="http://www.connaught.com/">Connaught Laboratories Limited</a> - fully-integrated biotechnology research company and vaccine manufacturer.

<li><a href="http://cps.bio.com/">Corning Pharmaceutical Services</a> - pharmaceutical and biotechnology drug development capabilities, provides job listings, abstracts, and a 'bio-cafe' bulletin board.

<li><a href="http://www.displaysystems.com/">Display Systems Biotechnology</a> - A new biotech company emerging from the scientific  community.

<li><a href="http://www.finnigan.com/">Finnigan Corporation</a> - manufactures analytical instruments such as mass spectrometers and gas chromatographs, used in areas such as pharmaceutical, biotechnology and environmental applications.

<li><a href="http://www.genetics.com/">Genetics Institute</a> - a biotechnology firm  pioneering in the development of innovative protein-based  therapeutics for the treatment of serious human medical  conditions.  

<li><a href="http://www.hemostat.com/">HemoStat Laboratories</a> - quality animal blood and serum for diagnostic, veterinary  and biotechnology applications.

<li><a href="HTTP://www.labmart.com/">Labmart</a> - provides application notes helping solve laboratory problems provided by manufacturers and scientists in chromatography, spectroscopy, separations, biotechnology and biopharmaceuticals.

<li><a href="http://www.luxnet.com/">LuxNet</a> - information for the biotechnology and pharmaceutical  industries. Searchable databases of consultants, contract  laboratories, and other service providers. 

<li><a href="http://www.millipore.com/">Millipore Corporation</a> - biotechnology, pharmaceutical, semiconductor, life science research and other industries.

<li><a href="http://www.novo.dk/">Novo Nordisk A/S</a> - Biotechnology-based manufacturer of pharmaceutical and industrial enzyme products.

<li><a href="http://www.omicronbio.com/">Omicron Biomedical Inc</a> - biotechnology company established 1982 providing specialty stable isotopes. 

<li><a href="http://www.cris.com/~biotech/paragon.html">Paragon Biotech WEBalog</a> - catalogue of biotechnology and molecular biology products and services.

<li><a href="http://www.pharmingen.com/">PharMingen</a> - biotechnology company that develops,  manufactures, and markets high quality, leading edge  products for biomedical research and in vitro  diagnostics.  

<li><a href="http://www.promega.com/">Promega Corporation</a> - supplier of biological reagents and systems in the worldwide biotechnology research products market

<li><a href="http://www.prozyme.com/">ProZyme, Inc</a> - a biotechnology company manufacturing specialty proteins for research and diagnostics.  

<li><a href="http://www.scbt.com/">Santa Cruz Biotechnology</a> - develops unique antibody reagents to facilitate studies in the area of signal transduction.

<li><a href="http://www.cancer.spectralbio.com/">Spectral Bioanalysis, Inc</a> - Doing research and analysis in the field of Biotechnology.  (in German)

<li><a href="http://www.access.digex.net/~regulate/">Trevigen, Inc</a> - Biotechnology company focusing on research reagents and kits for the study of DNA damage, gene repair and apoptosis.

<li><a href="http://www.zymark.com/">Zymark Corporation</a> - leader in the field of laboratory automation and robotics for use in the research and analytical laboratories in pharmaceutical, biotechnology, chemical, agriculture, and food industries.
</UL>
<HR>

<CENTER><B>Device Makers</B></CENTER>
<P>
<UL>
<li><a href="http://www.biotek.com/">Bio-Tek Instruments, Inc.</a> - instruments for calibration,  testing, and evaluation of patient related products.  

<li><a href="http://theedge.com//bioclave/">Bioclave Systems</a> - Biomedical and Biohazardous Sterilization Autoclave Systems.

<li><a href="http://www.bioplate.com/">Bioplate, Inc</a> - Display/describe cranial-maxillo-facial plates, screws,  instruments, sets.  

<li><a href="http://www.cortex.dk/">Cortex Technology</a> - High frequency ultrasound, cryosurgical equipment and  other dedicated instruments for dermatology.  

<li><a href="http://www.dibaind.com/">DIBA Industries</a> - manufacturers of biomedical tubing, pumps, and dispensers.  

<li><a href="http://www.edaptechnomed.com/">EDAP Technomed, Inc</a> - an international company dedicated to developing, manufacturing and marketing minimally invasive medical devices. Prostatron prostate treatment now FDA approved.  

<li><a href="http://www.ephi.com/">Electropharmacology, Inc</a> - EPi designs, markets and manufactures medical devices  utilizing pulsed radio frequency therapy for the  treatment of pain and edema.  

<li><a href="http://www.ns.net//telescan/">Global Cardiology Services</a> - Transtelephonic ECG(EKG) Systems and Analysis Services.

<li><a href="http://www.guidant.com/">Guidant Corporation</a> - therapeutic devices.

<li><a href="http://www.heron-med.com/">Heron Medical Technologies, Inc</a> - focusing it's products towards the on-the-spot cardiopulmonary monitoring needs of health care providers.

<li><a href="http://www.srv.net/~it/index.html">Idaho Technology</a> - Manufacturer of the Rapidcycler, the fastest  thermo-cycler on the market.  

<li><a href="http://www.realtime.net/intbiomedical/">International Biomedical</a> - manufacturer of medical products ranging from physiological monitoring systems to transport  incubators for infants to radiation-resistant surgical gloves.  

<li><a href="http://www.LeonhardLang.co.at/med/">Leonhard Lang Medizin-Technik</a> - manufactures the high quality Skintact line  of ECG electrodes, other bioelectrodes and accessories.  

<li><a href="http://www.microstamping.com/">Micro Stamping Corp</a> - ISO9002 certified company serving the metal stamping and medical device community  for over 50 years. 

<li><a href="http://www.minimitter.com/">Mini-Mitter</a> - Biotelemetry products for ambulatory, laboratory, or medical monitoring of physiological parameters such as temperature, heart rate, and activity. 

<li><a href="http://www.cris.com/~Nims/">Non-Invasive Monitoring Systems</a> - Makers of the RespiTrace Plus cardio-respiratory monitor and SomnoStar PT digital polysomnographic recorder. Both devices use patented RespiTrace technology to observe breathing.

<li><a href="http://www.NAD.com/">North American Drager</a> - NAD, Inc.is a leader in anesthesia delivery systems.  

<li><a href="http://www.pdcorp.com/">Precision Dynamics Corp.</a>

<li><a href="http://www.webcom.com/~mednet/clients/replica/replica.html">Replicatech, Inc.</a> - Replica Plating Apparatus of Various Sizes; Sewn Reusable Velveteen Squares; Velveteen Drying Racks; Prongers; Templaters. Classical and Molecular Genetics, Yeast, Bacteria. 

<li><a href="http://www.deltec.com/">SIMS Deltec, Inc</a> - manufacture of devices used in infusion therapy.

<li><a href="http://www.surgidev.com/">Surgidev Corporation</a> - a manufacturer and marketer of intraocular lenses and other eye surgery related products.

<li><a href="http://www.dmi.net/system21/">Systems 21 Sterilization, Inc.</a>

<li><a href="http://www.thermo.com/">Thermo Electron Corporation</a> - implantable  heart pumps, mammography systems, laser hair removal  systems, and more.  

<li><a href="http://www.hooked.net/thoratec/">Thoratec Laboratories Corporation</a>

<li><a href="http://www.fishnet.net/~ventrex/">Ventrex</a> - a manufacturer of reusable blood pressure transducer.

<li><a href="http://www.vyker.com/">Vyker Instruments</a> - A manufacturer and marketer of ENT reusable and disposable surgical instruments and kits.

<li><a href="http://www.vysis.com/">Vysis, Inc.</a> - Quality producer of DNA probes, reagents and imaging systems. 

<li><a href="http://www.zmi.com/">Zymed</a> - a manufacturer of medical monitors.</UL>
