<td width=195 height=25 bgcolor="#FFFFE0"><CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=3 FACE="Arial"><A HREF="http://www.socalbio.org/menu.htm">Return to Main Menu</A></FONT></B></CENTER></td>
</tr></table></CENTER><BR><BR>

<UL>
<li><A HREF="http://www.ajb.dni.us/">America's Job Bank</A>.

<LI><A HREF="http://www.biospace.com/sd/career/">BCC postings</A>: Job postings in biotechnology and biotechnology related companies from the Biospace Career Center</A>.

<li><A HREF="http://cns.bio.com/hr/hr_index.html">Career Center</A> from <A HREF="http://cns.bio.com/">Bio Online</A>.

<li><A HREF="http://www.careerpath.com/">CareerPath</A>.

<li><A HREF="http://www.careermag.com/careermag/">Career Magazine</A>.

<li><A HREF="http://www.careermosaic.com/cm/">Career Mosaic</A>.

<LI><A HREF="http://www.cell.com/cell/posi/index.html">Cell</A>: Positions advertized in Cell.

<li><A HREF="http://chronicle.merit.edu/.ads/.links.html">Job listings</A> from the Chronicle of Higher Learning.

<li><A HREF="http://dns.treknet.net/hcroaz/">Heathcare Recruiters</A>.

<li><A HREF="http://www.webcom.com/nccareer/">Jobs in North Carolina</A>.

<li><A HREF="http://www.mcc.ac.uk/pwmirror/pwm/pharmwebm.html">Jobs on PharmWeb</A>.

<li><A HREF="http://www.nationjob.com/medical/">Medical/Health Care Jobs</A>.

<li><A HREF="http://www.medsearch.com/">MedSearch Amercia</A>.

<li><A HREF="http://www.occ.com/occ/SearchAllJobs.html">Online Career Center</A>. 

<li><a href="http://www.jobbrowser.com">The Partners</a> Placement services for software 
developers/engineers in the biomedical industry.

<li><A HREF="http://pharminfo.com/pharmmall/PharmWeek/pharmweek.html">Pharmacy Week Jobs Listing</A>.

<LI><A HREF="http://www.informatik.uni-rostock.de/HUM-MOLGEN/positions/">Positions in Bioscience and Medicine</A>: listed in Human Molecular Genetics.  

<li><A HREF="http://www.aaas.org/science/jobnet/jobnet.htm">Science Global Career Network</A>: Science Magazine's list of jobs.

<LI><A HREF="http://www.the-scientist.library.upenn.edu/jobs.html">The Scientist</A>: Job listings from the Scientist posted bi-weekly.</UL>

