<!-- Page Title: Southern California Biomedical Council: Internet Utilities -->
<!-- HTML Author: Ahmed A. Enany              -->
<!-- Graphics: Ahmed A. Enany                 -->
<!-- Copyright owner: SCBC                    -->
<!-- E-Mail: scbc@socalbio.org                -->
<!-- **************************************** -->
<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Southern California Biomedical Council: Links to Internet Utilities</TITLE><Meta name="description" content="Various software utilities to maximize your use and enjoyment of the World Wide Web."></HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFF80">


<center><table>
<td>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE =5>SOUTHEN CALIFORNIA BIOMEDICAL COUNCIL</FONT></B></CENTER>
<BR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE =4><B>Links to Software to Maximize your Use and Enjoyment of the Internet</B></FONT></CENTER>
<BR><BR><BR>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=1 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=5 WIDTH=550>
<TD VALIGN=TEXTTOP bgcolor="#80FF80">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="/graph/tools.jpg" width=100 height=69 alt="Tools"></CENTER>
<FONT SIZE =4>The Internt is a fast growing, increasingly complex, and multi-dimensional space. It is becoming a domain, not only of text and graphics, but also of sound and motion. To maximize your use and enjoyment of the Internet, we bring you links to freeware or shareware utilities that will enable you to master all features of the World Wide Web. </FONT>
</Table></Center>
<HR>
<CENTER><table>
<td bgcolor="#FF8080">
<CENTER><ADDRESS><A HREF="MAILTO:scbc@socalbio.org"><FONT SIZE =4><B><I>Click here to suggest internet resources that we should add to this list</B></I></FONT></A></address><BR></CENTER>
</td></table></CENTER>
<HR>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE =5><B>Audio</B></FONT></CENTER><BR>
<P>
<UL><LI><a href="http://www.dspg.com/plugin.htm"><FONT SIZE =4><I>TrueSpeech Player</I></FONT></a>. This is a Player/Plug-in for Windows 95/NT.<BR> 

<LI><a href="http://www.abc.se/~m9303/"><I><FONT SIZE =4>WAVmaker</FONT></I></a>. WAVmaker 2.4 for Windows is the latest descendant of WAVmaker 1.0, the world's first Shareware MID to WAV rendering & Audio FX package. It has been awarded Top 20 Product Status by Clicked, the Elite Shareware Gallery. And, Dave loves us! <BR>

<LI><a href="http://www.realaudio.com/products/player2.0.html"><FONT SIZE =4><I>Real Audio Player</I></FONT></a>. RealAudio Player 2.0 brings live and on-demand audio to your desktop over Internet connections of 14.4 Kbps and faster.<BR>

<LI><a href="http://www.vocaltec.com/iwave.htm"><FONT SIZE =4><I>Internet Wave</I></FONT></a>. Internet Wave lets you listen to top quality, real-time audio through your favorite web browser.<BR>
</UL>

<HR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=5>E-mail</FONT></CENTER>
<UL><LI><a href="http://www.eudora.com/light.html"><FONT SIZE=4><I>Eudora Light</I></FONT></a>. This is one of the most widely used E-mail program that supports dial-up connections. 
<LI><a href="http://www.powerup.com.au/~lindsay/index.htm"><FONT SIZE=4><I>MailCat</I></FONT> </a>. Its features include POP,SMTP & MIME. Send & Receive Rich Text/Encrypted Messages with file attachments in the background, Auto dialing, RAS & DUN Support. Filing Cabinets, Mail & Highlighting Rules, Address Book with Groups, and Spell checker. 
<LI><a href=" http://www.bekkoame.or.jp/~carty/ "><FONT SIZE=4><I> Becky Internet Mail for Windows 95</I></FONT></a>.  This is a multi-featured E-mail client specialized for Windows 95. It handles multiple accounts, has advanced text editing capabilities.
</UL>
<HR>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE =5>File Compression/Decompression Utilities</FONT></B></CENTER>
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.pkware.com/"><FONT SIZE =4><I>PKZip</I></FONT></a>. This is the orginal Zip archiver. Available for Windows and Dos.<BR>
<LI><a href="http://www.winzip.com/download.htm"><FONT SIZE =4><I>WinZip</I></FONT></a>. A program that can compress/uncompress in a variety of formats including ZIP, ARJ,  and LHA. It even has the option to virus scan the file before you extract it! Supports Win 3.1 and 95/NT.<BR>
</UL>

<HR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE =5><B>Image Viewers</B></FONT></CENTER><BR>
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.corel.ca:80/corelcmx/"><I><FONT SIZE =4>CMX Viewer</FONT></I></a>. The CMX viewer from Corel Corporation. The Viewer, now available in beta, makes it possible for Internet users to view Corel CMX files (vector format) online as opposed to the traditional GIF or JPEG files (raster format) currently associated with Internet use.<BR>

<LI><a href="http://www.inso.com/consumer/qvp/quickv.htm"><I><FONT SIZE =4>Quick View Plus</FONT></I></a>. Quick View Plus (TM) helps you make the most of your new Windows 95 operating system. It transforms the Quick View feature in Windows 95 from a convenient utility to a powerful productivity tool. Both are based on award-winning Outside In viewing technology. <BR>

<LI><a href=" http://www.compcore.com/testdriv.htm"><FONT SIZE =4><I>SoftPEG</I></FONT></a>. SoftPEG allows you to play back MPG (MPEG) graphics files.<BR>

<LI><a href="http://www.photodex.com/cpic.htm"><FONT SIZE =4><I>CompuPic</I></FONT></a>. A  powerful graphics browser for Windows to view, convert, thumbnail, catalog, adjust, enhance, and crop images.<BR>

<LI><a href="http://www.mindworkshop.com/alchemy/gww.html"><FONT SIZE =4><I>Graphic Workshop</I></FONT></a>. A shareware for conversion between different image formats.<BR>

<LI><a href="http://www.redshift.com/~arcatpet/"><FONT SIZE =4><I>Image Viewer</I></FONT></a>. A viewer/printer of BMP, GIF, JPEG, PCX, PNG, and TIFF graphic files.<BR>

<LI><a href="http://world.std.com/~mmedia/lviewp.html"><I><FONT SIZE =4>LView Pro</FONT></I></a>. A shareware graphics viewer that provides multiple-open and slideshow. Can also create transparent GIF files, and supports lots of image formats. <BR>
</ul>

<HR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=5><B>Internet Browsing Utilities</B></FONT></CENTER>
<UL><LI><a href="http://www.cyberpatrol.com "> Cyber Patrol</a>. This is one of the widely used programs to manage access to web sites on the Web. It enables parents or teachers to block access to adult-oriented material on the Internet.

<LI><a href="http://arachnid.qdeck.com/qdeck/products/wc20/">Quarterdeck's Web Compass</a>.  WebCompass gives you all the information you need to use the Web to your advantage. It organizes the vast amount of information on the Web helps you to stop wasting time and put an end to frustrating searches. WebCompass is an intelligent program that creates "on the fly summaries" of Web Pages. It doesn't just copy information from search engines but actually looks at the pages and writes a unique summary for that page.<B><FONT FACE="MODERN"> (Highly recommended)</FONT></B></UL>

<HR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE =5><B>Netscape Utilities</B></FONT></CENTER><BR>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.ffg.com/grabnet.html"> <FONT SIZE =4><I>GrabNet Shareware</I></FONT></A>. Captures URL, text and images from Netscape sessions.<BR>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.isysdev.com/hindsite.html"><FONT SIZE =4><I>HindSite</I></FONT></a>. This program automatically indexes all web sites you have visited so you can go back to them.<BR>

<LI><A HREF="http://home.netscape.com/"><I><FONT SIZE =4>NetScape Power Pack</FONT></I></a>. Adds four components to your Netscape Browser: CyberSpell for mail, Smart Marks for bookmarking, Netscape Chat and Symentac's Norton AntiVirus scanner.<BR>
<LI><a href="http://www.ffg.com/whacker.html"><FONT SIZE =4><I>Web Whacker Shareware</I></FONT></a>. WebWhacker downloads entire Web pages or groups of pages, including text (HTML) and images, and stores them on the local desktop. The downloaded pages and images are relinked locally for later browsing without an Internet connection.<BR>
</UL>
<HR>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE =5>On-line News</FONT></B></CENTER>
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.infomkt.ibm.com/ht2/ticker.htm"><FONT SIZE=4><I>infoMarket NewsTicker for Windows95</I></FONT></a>. A news reader from IBM, and it works like a stock ticker bar.  
<LI><a href="http://www.netcontrols.com"><FONT SIZE=4><I>My Yahoo! News Ticker</I></FONT></a>. Get the latest news, sports, stock quotes on the Web. 
<LI><a href="http://webmax.com/productinfo/freedl.html "><FONT SIZE=4> <I>Web Max TV</I></FONT></a>.  Automatically brings news and information on the Web directly to your computer screen.
<LI><a href="http://www.scroller.com "><FONT SIZE=4><I>WorldFlash 32-bit [formerly NewsFlash]</I></FONT></a>.  A new internet, online news service.
</UL>
<HR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=5><B>Teleconferencing on the Internet</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL><LI><a href="http://magenta.com/cyberphone "><FONT SIZE=4> <I>CyberPhone 32-bit</I></FONT> </a>. This is an Internet Telephone software that permits long distance telephone-like conversations on the Internet.

<LI><a href="http://dsp.ee.cuhk.edu.hk/proj/gtalk/welcome.html "><FONT SIZE=4> <I>GatherTalk for Windows 95</I></FONT> </a>. It allows teleconferencing on Internet. It can support 3 people conferencing using 14.4kbps modems and 5 people conferencing using 28.8kbps modems. 

<LI><a href="http://www.vdolive.com/vdophone/ "><FONT SIZE=4><I> VDOPhone</I></FONT></a>.  Use VDOPhone to place a call to, or
receive a call from, any other Internet user with a VDOPhone and transmit two-way COLOR video and audio, or audio only, over modem connections to Internet at speeds of 14.4kbps and up. 
                                                                         
<LI><a href="http://viablesoftware.com/viatalk/"> <FONT SIZE=4><I>ViaTalk Conference for Windows 95</I></FONT> </a> This is another teleconferencing program. The package includes a complete chat client, Email client, FTP client, and the new SurfSilly Bookmark bar for automatically creating and organizing WWW Bookmark lists using your browser.
</UL>
<HR>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE =5>Text Readers</FONT></B></CENTER>
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.adobe.com/acrobat/"><FONT SIZE =4><I>Adobe Acrobat Reader</I></FONT></a>. Free viewer for Portable Document Format (PDF) documents. 
<LI><a href="http://www.twcorp.com/viewer.htm"><I><FONT SIZE =4>Envoy Viewer</FONT></I></a>. Free viewer for portable documents created with WordPerfect Envoy.
</UL>

<HR>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE =5>UseNet Utilities</FONT></B></CENTER>
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.dlcwest.com"><FONT SIZE =4><I>JobFind Shareware</I></FONT></a>. A UseNet News Reader Software that automatically scans newsgroup for job postings through keywords called a Watch List, eliminating unwanted jobs with Kill Lists. <BR>
<LI><a href="http://www.intel.com/iaweb/aplets/newsread.htm"><FONT SIZE =4><I>Smart News Reader</I></FONT></a> A UseNet news reader supporting MIME, sorting and "auot-link" (converts plain news article to linked documents).  <BR>
<LI><a href="http://www.primenet.com/~smbaker/sbnews/sbnews.html"><FONT SIZE =4><I>SBNews/News-Robot</I></FONT></a>. Designed to automatically download and uudecode files from binary newsgroups. <BR>
<LI><a href="http://www.teleport.com/~magoldsm/winstock/index.html"><I><FONT SIZE =4>WinStock Shareware</FONT></I></a>. A stock market tracking program.<BR>
</UL>

<HR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE =5><B>Video</B></FONT></CENTER><BR>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.portal.com/~dwalker/dirhome.html"><FONT SIZE =4><I>Director Viewer</I></FONT></a>. Free viewer for Director files, a MPEG-like movie format. 

<LI><a href="http://quicktime.apple.com/"><FONT SIZE =4><I>QuickTime for Windows</I></FONT></a>. Free player for Apple quick time movies. 

<LI><A HREF="http://www.macromedia.com/shockwave/"><FONT SIZE =4><I>Shock Wave</I></FONT></a> A Netscape plug-in viewer for Director files, a multimedia movie format.

<LI><a href="http://www.vivo.com/vivoactive/player_form.html"><FONT SIZE=4><I>VivoActive Player</I></FONT></a>. This is a popular web browser plug-in for viewing streaming video on the web. 

</UL>

<HR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=5><B>Virus Detection and Cleaning Utilities</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL><LI><a href="http://www.ffg.com/pcproducts/avirus.html"><FONT SIZE=4><I>AllMicro Anti-Virus for Windows 95</I></FONT> </a>. An anti-virus software that scans your hard disk in seconds to detect over 8,0000 commonly known viruses.

<LI><a href="http://www.mcafee.com/ "><FONT SIZE=4><I>Mcafee Viruscan Scan</I></FONT> </a>. A virus scanner.

<LI><a href="http://www.sophos.com/sweep/sweep95.html"><FONT SIZE=4><I>SWEEP Virus Detection for Windows95 </I></FONT></a>. Provides virus detection using the advanced Virus Description Language (VDL), which allows the distribution of urgent updates by any means, including fax. 

<LI><a href="http://www.safe.net/ "> <FONT SIZE=4><I>VirusNet for Windows 95</I></FONT></a>. It detects 7933 viruses including Word Macro, Boza and PKZIP 300 trojan. 
</UL>
<HR>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE =5>Winsock</FONT></B></CENTER>
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://members.aol.com/rron222/swap16.htm"><FONT SIZE =4><I>CT Swapper</I></FONT></a>. This program automates the process of swapping various WINSOCK.DLL files for those using more than one Internet service provider with your default Web Browser. <BR>
</UL>

<HR>
